sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor V as Visitor
    participant UI as /signup
    participant Z as Zod schema
    participant SA as signUp action
    participant SB as Supabase Auth
    participant LP as logPolicyAcknowledgment
    participant T as policy_acknowledgments
    participant E as Email confirm

    V->>UI: name + email + password + tickbox
    UI->>Z: validate (acknowledgePolicies must be true)
    Z-->>UI: parsed payload
    UI->>SA: invoke server action

    SA->>SB: auth.signUp(email, password, name)
    SB-->>SA: data.user.id
    SB->>E: send confirm email (PKCE link)

    par log T&Cs version
        SA->>LP: { userId, docTypes:['terms','privacy'], context:'signup' }
        LP->>T: insert 1 row per doc<br/>(version + IP + UA)
    and continue happy path
        SA-->>UI: { redirectTo: '/verify-email' }
    end

    Note over V,E: User clicks email link
    V->>E: /auth/confirm?code=...
    E-->>V: PKCE exchange, set session
    V->>UI: redirect to /account
    Note over V: Future signin auto-clears<br/>user_metadata.deactivated_at
